Confirm all nails have been removed from slab soffits

Confirm that all balcony and wet area set downs have been reviewed and rectified due to incorrect setouts or issues of depth

Confirm all caulking to precast (both horizontal & vertical) is complete
Confirm all precast props and excess material removed from level
Confirm that surveyor Benchmark and grid lines are visible on slab If not contact surveyor and re-instate
Confirm that all structural defects are rectified and signed off
Conduct walk with Finishes Foreman of entire floor, and agree handover
